## 🎯 7. Agent Skills (SKILL.md)

Skills sao instrucoes reutilizaveis carregadas sob demanda via `skill()` tool.
Local: `.opencode/skills/<name>/SKILL.md`

### 7.1 Skills NeoCortex ativas
| Skill | Descricao | MCP Tools usadas |
|---|---|---|
| `nc-validate` | Pipeline R6 completo (ruff+mypy+bandit+yaml+mdc+json+@LOCKS+secret) | neocortex_governance (yaml.validate, mdc.validate, secret.scan, naming.check, lock.validate, ssot.diff) |
| `nc-lint` | Rapido: ruff + mypy + pyright em .py | ruff check/format + mypy |
| `nc-audit` | Auditoria 3 camadas FR-173 | neocortex_governance (compliance.report, audit.full) + neocortex_state (regression.check, checkpoint.list) + neocortex_health (server.health) |
| `nc-handoff` | Gera handoff YAML NC-DS-*-handoff-*.yaml | neocortex_governance (handoff.create) |
| `nc-boot-sync` | Sincroniza @BOOT + catalog refresh | neocortex_governance (bootup.sync, catalog.refresh) |
| `nc-ssot-update` | Atualiza @SSOT com changelog | neocortex_governance (ssot.diff, naming.check) |

### 7.2 Pipeline de skills (ordem fixa)
```
nc-lint → nc-validate → nc-ssot-update → nc-handoff → nc-boot-sync
```

