## 🛠️ 8. Custom Tools (TypeScript)

Ferramentas nativas TypeScript em `.opencode/tools/*.ts`.
Chamam scripts Python existentes do NeoCortex.

| Tool | Descricao | Chama |
|---|---|---|
| `nc-lint.ts` | ruff check + mypy via Bun.$ | ruff check --fix |
| `nc-audit.ts` | Auditoria 3 camadas | NC-CORE-FR-173-mcp-audit-3-levels.py |
| `nc-handoff.ts` | Gera handoff YAML via Bun.write | 09-audit-logs/ |
| `nc-sync.ts` | Bootup sync + catalog refresh | NC-SCR-FR-066 + NC-SCR-FR-064 |
| `nc-validate.ts` | Validacao multi-tipo (py+yaml+mdc+json) | ruff + py_compile + yaml.safe_load |

